# unknownPersonViewDelegate

**Instance Property**

The unknown-person view controller delegate.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor unowned(unsafe) var unknownPersonViewDelegate: (any ABUnknownPersonViewControllerDelegate)? { get set }
```

## Discussion

The delegate must adopt the [doc://com.apple.addressbookui/documentation/AddressBookUI/ABUnknownPersonViewControllerDelegate] protocol.

## Responding to View Controller Interactions

- **ABUnknownPersonViewControllerDelegate**: The methods you use to respond to events in an unknown person view controller.
